PRIVACY POLICY FOR KARAOKIFY TV PLAYER
Last Updated: May 24, 2026

1. INTRODUCTION
Welcome to KaraOkify TV Player. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information in our Android TV application.

2. INFORMATION COLLECTION AND USE
KaraOkify TV Player is designed to serve as a high-quality display and playback hub for your karaoke sessions.
* Personal Data: We do not collect personally identifiable information (such as your email or phone number) on our servers. Any names entered for the "Singer" field are received from the remote phone and stored locally on your TV device only.
* Performance Data: Performance scores received from the connected remote phone are stored locally on your TV device to maintain a session history and leaderboard.

3. PERMISSIONS AND HARDWARE USAGE
To provide its core features, KaraOkify TV Player requires the following permissions:
* Bluetooth (BLUETOOTH_CONNECT, SCAN, ADVERTISE): Used to receive song requests, control commands (Play/Pause/Skip), and scoring data from the KaraOkify phone app (Remote Mode).
* Location (ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION): Required by the Android system to enable Bluetooth communication and discovery. We do not track or store your actual physical location.
* Internet: Used to stream karaoke videos via the embedded YouTube player.

4. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
Our app uses the following third-party services which may collect information used to identify you:
* YouTube API Services: Used to provide karaoke video content. By using this app, you are also bound by the Google Privacy Policy (https://www.google.com/policies/privacy).
* Google AdMob: Used to display advertisements. AdMob may collect and use data according to its own privacy policy (https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads).

5. DATA STORAGE AND SECURITY
* All session data (Queue, History, and Leaderboard) is stored locally on the TV device using internal storage.
* Session history and leaderboard data are automatically reset daily at 7:00 AM to maintain performance and privacy.
* Because all data is local, deleting the app will permanently remove all your saved session history.

6. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY
Our app does not knowingly collect any personal information from children. If you are a parent and aware that your child has provided us with personal data, please contact us.

7. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. You are advised to review this page periodically for any changes.

8. CONTACT US
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at: support@karaokify.com
